    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is offset by the direct correspondence of the validation scenario to the COU, the multi-laboratory test dataset (N=11), and normalized error metrics well within acceptance bounds for all three primary QoIs. The overall credibility package is judged sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for this Class II device application.",
